Primarily stationed aboard [[Galactic Empire/Legends|Imperial]] [[Capital ship/Legends|capital ships]] and [[Space station/Legends|space stations]], '''Imperial Fleet Regiments''' consisting of [[Imperial Navy Trooper/Legends|Imperial Navy troopers]] would, alongside [[Stormtrooper/Legends|stormtrooper]] [[Regiment/Legends|regiments]], handle the security aboard the [[Starship/Legends|ship]] or space station as well as assist in [[Planet/Legends|planetary]] assault missions.

They wore [[Color/Legends|black]] uniforms and helmets, and carried side arms.

